  "description_snippet": "Security Bug\n\n-------------------------\n\nVULNERABILITY DETAILS\nAn attacker can exploit a combination of opening a Picture-in-Picture (PiP) window and a hidden popup behind it. By manipulating the focus onto the concealed popup, an attacker can hijack keypresses when a user interacts with the website"
